            "description": "➕ **Create a new product.**\n\nMethod: POST\nBody: JSON with product details.\n\n✅ Expected Response: 201 Created with the new product object including generated ID.\n\n💡 Practice: Add more fields, try missing required fields, change categories.\n\n⚠️ Note: This is a fake/mock API — data won't actually persist."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Update Product (Full - PUT)",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/products/1",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["products", "1"]
            },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"title\": \"Updated Product Title\",\n  \"description\": \"Fully updated product description.\",\n  \"price\": 999.99,\n  \"discountPercentage\": 15,\n  \"rating\": 4.8,\n  \"stock\": 50,\n  \"brand\": \"UpdatedBrand\",\n  \"category\": \"laptops\",\n  \"thumbnail\": \"https://via.placeholder.com/300\"\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "description": "✏️ **Fully replace a product (PUT).**\n\nMethod: PUT\nURL Param: Product ID\nBody: Complete product JSON (all fields)\n\n✅ Expected Response: 200 OK with updated product.\n\n💡 PUT replaces the entire resource. Compare with PATCH which only updates specific fields.\n\n📌 Difference — PUT vs PATCH:\n- PUT: Replace everything\n- PATCH: Update only what you send"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Update Product (Partial - PATCH)",
          "request": {
            "method": "PATCH",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/products/1",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["products", "1"]
            },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"price\": 1299.99,\n  \"stock\": 200\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "description": "🩹 **Partially update a product (PATCH).**\n\nMethod: PATCH\nURL Param: Product ID\nBody: Only the fields you want to change\n\n✅ Expected Response: 200 OK with merged/updated product.\n\n💡 Only send the fields you want to update — other fields remain unchanged.\n\n📌 Difference — PUT vs PATCH:\n- PUT: Replace everything\n- PATCH: Update only what you send"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Delete Product",
          "request": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "header": [],
